ml_tags: In Memory of You were our greatest ecological asset, singlehandedly eradicating millions of noxious weeds in the Nillumbik Shire. For your tireless advocacy and care for our bushland. You toiled day after day, year after year, decade after decade. Humble, devoted and selfless, expecting nothing in return. 24/3/1945 - 9/8/2021 Robert Bell Thank you Robert If only there were more like you.
